openDLX v1.0 - A DLX/MIPS processor simulator.
Copyright (C) 2013 The openDLX project, University of Augsburg

Core contributors: Stefan Metzlaff, Alexander Vogelgsang, and Nico Krezic-Luger
Contributors: Arne Garbade, Patrick Lehner, Mia Metzler

Project URL: <http://sourceforge.net/projects/opendlx>
Development branch: <https://github.com/smetzlaff/openDLX>


----------------------------
Requirements
----------------------------

- Java 8
- Maven for development

----------------------------
Building
----------------------------

1. mvn package


----------------------------
Usage
----------------------------

For GUI version:
  java -jar openDLX.jar [-g]
For non interactive version:
  java -jar openDLX.jar -c config_file.cfg
For help message:
  java -jar openDLX.jar -h
About & license information:
  java -jar openDLX.jar -about

